OHOS::UISwipeView::OnSwipeListener
==================================

**Overview**\ 
--------------

**Related Modules:**

`Graphic <graphic.md>`__

**Description:**

Represents a listener for changes of the swipe view.

This is an inner class of `UISwipeView <ohos-uiswipeview.md>`__. It
contains a callback function to be invoked when the swipe view state
changes.
